                                                                <customfield id="customfield_12310192" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>By setting hbase.resolve.hostnames.on.failure to false you can reduce the number of dns name resolutions that a client will do. However if machines leave and come back with different ip&amp;#39;s the changes will not be noticed by the clients. So only set hbase.resolve.hostnames.on.failure to false if your cluster dns is not changing while clients are connected.</customfieldvalue>

                        </customfieldvalues>
